{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"7584c678a5","title":"戚本禹王力接见湖北代表座谈纪要","origin":"1967.5.17外贸部井冈山公社资料组翻印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1d345bea2c","index":0,"year":1967,"month":5,"day":15,"articleId":"7584c678a5"}],"tags":[{"id":"04d5170184","name":"湖北文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"1ae024ca96","name":"革命大联合","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"20ebde32a6","name":"王力","type":"人物"},{"id":"40ffd466ef","name":"武斗","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"4172b5fa3c","name":"九·一三事件","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"4206ce6bf3","name":"红卫兵运动","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"4d9a2ea656","name":"陈再道","type":"人物"},{"id":"57434e107b","name":"戚本禹","type":"人物"},{"id":"70a1e48626","name":"军队支左","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"7aac50a8c5","name":"文艺战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"82305e518c","name":"江青","type":"人物"},{"id":"8b05ac46d8","name":"王任重","type":"人物"},{"id":"aa9434abe4","name":"北京文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"ef71f03227","name":"中央文革","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"9014e20fdf","name":"戚本禹"},{"id":"fa147b61e7","name":"王力"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"5d16dd4d2d","type":"title","text":"戚本禹王力接见湖北代表座谈纪要","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"cd7203cf65","type":"authors","text":"戚本禹王力","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"a93e10a03e","type":"appellation","text":"〖时间：1967年5月15日下午3：30分－5：50；地点：政协礼堂东池会议厅。接见单位：新华工、新华农、新湖大、二司、工总、九一三、一始工人造反司令部、黄石代表、天门代表、解放军文艺代表团、卫校代表、三司红色造反团、三司。〗","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"aa54f40852","type":"paragraph","text":"（在我新华农进来以前，三司以在里面，新华工、新湖大等进来后为了前面的座位和三司吵了起来，因为前面靠桌子的座位每一单位一个记录者，可三司四人座在前面，要他们退下来二个，让工人和解放军他们不让，结果吵了起来。正在吵得很凶的时候，王力、戚本禹进来）","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"c4d14b33c4","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：你们吵，吵我就不接见你们了。（笑着说）","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"c68f822510","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：（坐下后）噢！我见过你们一次，（看见代表们带的袖章后说）新华工、新华农……（这时新华工、新华农、新湖大等单位纷纷献了袖章，新华工代表把“新华工”别在王力同志的军装胸前）。你们给了，你们没有了。上次我说要见你们一次，一直没有时间。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"2bb7a7c459","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：（这时武汉军事院校代表进来了）他们都是被抓过的，都进过牢的。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"defd74a90e","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：那不要紧。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"0fed9776dc","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：王力同志来见你们。（介绍王力。）","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"4b433b0be9","type":"paragraph","text":"王：这是戚本禹同志。（鼓掌）","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"a67f6998a0","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：我们今天来不能解决任何问题，我们主要是来调查研究的，今天来的有没有两派？","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"d1fee36234","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：有，有三司的！","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"1020460bd6","type":"paragraph","text":"王力：刚才不是在吵架嘛（指他们进来时我们和三司吵架）。","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"51f8041ff1","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：（介绍刚才吵架的问题）略。","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"28a027715a","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：这点事你们就吵，吵得不可开交，你们的造反精神太大了。（笑）我五点半还有会，现在三点半，开到五点半。你们商量商量怎么开，他们谈听你们的意见。上次已经给记者（谈）过这些问题，武汉的问题主要靠武汉的老百姓解决。我不讲了，你们谈。","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"e3f64c904d","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：我们先谈一个多钟头，然后请首长指示。（三司指示要两派各谈一半时间。）","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"a43b3467c9","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：你们可以多谈点。","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"45582db723","type":"paragraph","text":"王：你们现在就谈吧！","index":17,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"b1c994ce43","type":"paragraph","text":"武汉代表：首先让我们敬祝我们心中最红最红的红太阳毛主席万寿无疆！万寿无疆！祝林副统帅身体永远健康，永远健康！（鼓掌）","index":18,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"d4e65780ca","type":"paragraph","text":"王：你叫什么名字？","index":19,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"c28d543ca9","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：（介绍）叫某某某。","index":20,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"c3a220cfae","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：你们呆在这里不好，要和群众一起战斗。","index":21,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"bc8a1a4933","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：首长做指示后，我们马上回去。","index":22,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"dff5b9adf4","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：今天来两派。","index":23,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"7088cf5f9e","type":"paragraph","text":"（武汉革命造反派开始向首长汇报武汉地区资本主义复辟的情况，武汉运动资本主义复辟的表现，革命造反派惨遭残酷镇压，抓、取缔……当谈到军队内部问题，军区机关24个组织被打成反革命组织，抓了200多人，谈到雷达兵问题时。）","index":24,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"72e08e28d3","type":"paragraph","text":"王：雷达兵学校抓人是什么时间？","index":25,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"76d33b637f","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：3月21日","index":26,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"a1724615d6","type":"paragraph","text":"王：这是从2月开始的？（指武汉抓人，搞资本主义复辟。）","index":27,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"c3a5f7b6c1","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：二月就开始了。","index":28,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"a4a1f9105b","type":"paragraph","text":"（同学接着谈，当谈到武汉“二八”声明后，抓人时。）","index":29,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"d5af6626c2","type":"paragraph","text":"王：武汉抓了多少？","index":30,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"b25442b1ed","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：2600多人。","index":31,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"2bb83bda2c","type":"paragraph","text":"（当同学谈到敢死队，抓了人坐牢，又指着敢死队人说，坐牢挨打的人来了。这时敢死队战士起来。戚、王连连点头。）","index":32,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"e4f451983e","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：当谈到二司问题时，军区谭（震林）式人物说：学生现在不抓以后要抓。","index":33,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"e6152660c5","type":"paragraph","text":"（王叹了一口气。）","index":34,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"3e100c8928","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：当谈到抓人时，他们还说抓人这是通过江青同志的。","index":35,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"34641b25b0","type":"paragraph","text":"王：（微笑）哈，县里什么时候开始抓的。","index":36,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"f2a295bcb9","type":"paragraph","text":"（同学谈韩东山，黄石，天门问题，论韩东山。）","index":37,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"89ae61c800","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：我知道。","index":38,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"1045bfe0e7","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：天门二人来等见首长，可是没见到，正准备走时，家里又来人说家里又在抓人。","index":39,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"3ea5fcd014","type":"paragraph","text":"（王点了头。）","index":40,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"f339423eeb","type":"paragraph","text":"同志：有的逼的妻离子散，有的急得跑到新疆！","index":41,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"597e7be21a","type":"paragraph","text":"（王长叹一口气。）","index":42,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"b9e9e3778c","type":"paragraph","text":"（同学：当谈到某某某地一个人头上钉了三颗钉子，可在上吊后派出所还检查说，这是自杀的，同学说：这不很怪？那有这样事？）","index":43,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"b1de2c622f","type":"paragraph","text":"（王摆头。）","index":44,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"c555cfd5b9","type":"paragraph","text":"（同学谈到绍宇锐时。）","index":45,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"e4feddd657","type":"paragraph","text":"同学（介绍说）：就是武汉的“红卫兵”。","index":46,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"fb97eabc32","type":"paragraph","text":"（戚点点头。）","index":47,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"966488cc81","type":"paragraph","text":"（同学谈到北京有联动，武汉有几动：特动、军动……）","index":48,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"e8c8c8fa87","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：（轻微地）哼！","index":49,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"5dd1b2d5d4","type":"paragraph","text":"（同志谈到一张保字号的反动大字报，共48张时，念：“周总理是在毛主席身边的定时炸弹……。”）","index":50,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"b7164a0aa0","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：（打断话）不要念了，这我看了。（这时王力接过看）","index":51,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"657f2f2898","type":"paragraph","text":"同：三字兵还说王任重“秋后算账”提的过早了，王任重是内部问题。","index":52,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"56910dd854","type":"paragraph","text":"（王力轻微地笑。）","index":53,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"332b432379","type":"paragraph","text":"同：前几天在北京抓了武汉的特动，他们偷东西，搞到北京来了，","index":54,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"5276040fb1","type":"paragraph","text":"（王力笑……。）","index":55,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"e351a4e99b","type":"paragraph","text":"同：武汉特动尽是高干子弟组成，王任重儿子，张体学女儿，韩东山儿子。","index":56,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"1b274fedcd","type":"paragraph","text":"（王力点点头。）","index":57,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"418318101b","type":"paragraph","text":"同：有的特动说。过去我爸爸用这（铁鞭）打鬼子，我今天用它打思想兵。","index":58,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"76f2c62574","type":"paragraph","text":"（王力点点头。）","index":59,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"950699b133","type":"paragraph","text":"同：解放军战士、武汉军区某些人、武装部都散布“秋后算账”论。","index":60,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"f3636078ea","type":"paragraph","text":"（王力连连点头。）","index":61,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"e069f0f7d8","type":"paragraph","text":"（同学谈到武汉军区内有一直站在毛主席路线的一边，如某某某。）","index":62,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"4afaf2cee4","type":"paragraph","text":"王力：谁？","index":63,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"b6637beded","type":"paragraph","text":"同：张静。","index":64,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"0ea76340f6","type":"paragraph","text":"王力：是什么人？","index":65,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"6833cf2e3a","type":"paragraph","text":"同：湖北军区副政委。","index":66,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"f9403258f5","type":"paragraph","text":"同：军区内坏蛋还造谣，如：通过……（不清）给新华工三点指示。","index":67,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"2a3eb330bb","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：（举手）我知道。","index":68,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"f8d7ed1d06","type":"paragraph","text":"同：江青同志讲话他们篡改（解放军举起材料给戚看）","index":69,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"f432c86235","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：点头。","index":70,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"f094475933","type":"paragraph","text":"同：陈再道从北京回汉，武斗不减少，反而增加，三天之内发生150多次。","index":71,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"710597455f","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：点头。","index":72,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"2e800049a9","type":"paragraph","text":"同：谈韩东山在黄……（不清）","index":73,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"8a6e07bae4","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：算了，不谈了，你们材料我看了。","index":74,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"39b8c333ad","type":"paragraph","text":"同：（这时代表讲完了）我讲（新华工）。","index":75,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"a910644630","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：让不同意见发表，不是有个三司吗？三司在这里！","index":76,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"b03f5391bd","type":"paragraph","text":"（三司代表发言，略）","index":77,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"73ab4919b3","type":"paragraph","text":"（三司造反派发言，略）","index":78,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"d3cf6b9a8d","type":"paragraph","text":"（二司发言，略）","index":79,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"881e103769","type":"paragraph","text":"（新华工、新华农、新湖大联合发言，略）","index":80,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"3255f431d7","type":"paragraph","text":"（工人总部发言，略）","index":81,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"16b4379d47","type":"paragraph","text":"（卫生学校发言，略）","index":82,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"4a0e53020e","type":"paragraph","text":"（解放军发言，略）","index":83,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"93003cfa6e","type":"paragraph","text":"解放军代表：斗他们时，腰弯90度（作姿式）","index":84,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"83159d0ce7","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：点头。","index":85,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"a66e8abe29","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：你们100多少人？","index":86,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"4f9a9418de","type":"paragraph","text":"解：抓77个人，共164人。","index":87,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"41c82923ed","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：武汉卫生学校。","index":88,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"0daa2f9975","type":"paragraph","text":"（解放军代表念一份血书，是一位解放军同志的，念完后交给首长。）","index":89,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"ba84fc987e","type":"paragraph","text":"（戚接过血书，王力点点头，接过看。）","index":90,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"5fbe96f267","type":"paragraph","text":"解：你看直升机散的传单。","index":91,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"48d010427d","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：是，是，是……。（接过）","index":92,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"b69a0f5581","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹：今天我们听了你们很多话，看了很多材料，我们很感谢大家。王力跟我看了材料，听了你们发言，我们有三个意见（不代表中央文革）","index":93,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"c4ef746eeb","type":"paragraph","text":"第一、湖北来京工人、学生，赶紧回去到群众中去，参加运动，中央对湖北问题正在调查研究，以后再解决。如果中央再需要你们来反映情况，你们再来。（问：你们来了多少人？）（答：五、六百人）你们赶快回去，因为你们都是勤务员，中央对这个问题，正在研究。","index":94,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"ad7d717c6c","type":"paragraph","text":"第二、军区在支工、支农、支左中是有成绩的，但也有缺点错误，这主要是在支左上。现在他们正在改正这些缺点错误，我们和你们都需要再看一看，有缺点错误都要改正，不要越陷越深，改正了就好了。有意见可以说，方式要适当。（指军区）希望你们回去根据中央的指示和湖北的情况形势斗争制定斗争方案、政策。","index":95,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"7b83f7f59f","type":"paragraph","text":"第三、应当坚决执行军委十条命令、中央对安徽问题五条命令、五条指示。凡是错误地打成反革命的组织，应一律平反。逮捕的，应立即释放。各群众组织应当整风，着重自我批评（王力：着重自我批评。）整顿思想，整顿组织，整顿作风（王力：要掌握斗争的大方向）要掌握斗争的大方向，各群众组织之间的争论只许摆事实，讲道理，不许武斗，不许打砸抢。","index":96,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"7aa84db72a","type":"paragraph","text":"一华工同志问：陈再道大字报上街可以不可以？","index":97,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"71abcdebd5","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：可以采取其他方式，送上门。","index":98,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"191b70a88e","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：“打倒陈大麻子”是反动口号。","index":99,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"4ddfdf70a9","type":"paragraph","text":"王力：以后不要这样喊就行了。我们的意见你们可能不满足，但我们只能讲这么一点，我们还要调查研究，以后解决湖北问题时再请你们来。","index":100,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"},{"id":"78d0697008","type":"paragraph","text":"（以上稿指示根据首长和我战友对话一节一节合起来的，所以当中有不全之处，有错误我们本人负责，供参考用）","index":101,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5"}],"page":{"id":"0e7dca159d","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7584c678a5","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}